{"tid":1847372,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大家有冇諗過社區大爆發後, 醫護應該點做？","createTime":"2020-01-28T04:46:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T16:51:47.000Z","uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"662bff1af21609212a871521b282d26046a73ae9","tid":1847372,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T04:46:04.000Z","msg":"而家林奠拖字訣, 等有香港人受感染<br />\n咁就可以企喺道德高地指責醫護企圖罷工<br />\n係連香港人都棄之不顧, 咁醫護就會諗起碼都救香港人而返工<br />\n最終負荷唔到中招就令更多醫護疊埋心水返工救人<br />\n林奠最尾大計係幫習近平奶乾淨D屎,<br />\n黑醫護又死咁一兩成, 光明正大引入支那醫護<br />\n又可以對外宣稱全民齊心抗疫成功, 一石三鳥！<br />\n<br />\n希望大家諗定PlanB最壞打算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個人覺得醫護未實施罷工前, 民間疫情會大爆發, 港共執死雞聯合今日民建聯所講即時封關, 再逼醫護返工。<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得到嗰個時刻請唔好有咩道德包伏, 支那人就唔撚同佢醫。因為你要抱著性命風險去醫佢, 隨時攻擊你嘅保護裝備<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有咩PlanB討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecb35dfdca3ddae456b0ff4b4cb9227bf24e54c6","tid":1847372,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T04:46:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人人毒撚</span>"},{"pid":"f064eda4c7b5b25459751ead36ef63b47b0d2e15","tid":1847372,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T04:47:53.000Z","msg":"請手廣傳, 想問下醫護大爆發有咩睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申你地即時辭職一樣支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a90000833d2c856153e6ed0bf8bc0345bae0565e","tid":1847372,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f064eda4c7b5b25459751ead36ef63b47b0d2e15","tid":1847372,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T04:47:53.000Z","msg":"請手廣傳, 想問下醫護大爆發有咩睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申你地即時辭職一樣支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 